TITLE: Migrating Custom Wallet List for RainbowKit v0.7.x
DESCRIPTION: Code diff showing how to migrate from the namespaced wallet imports to individual wallet imports for RainbowKit v0.7.x. This change reduces bundle size by allowing tree-shaking of unused wallets.
