TITLE: Integrating Enkrypt Wallet with RainbowKit in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Example code showing how to integrate Enkrypt wallet into a RainbowKit application by importing the wallet connector and adding it to the connectors list.
SOURCE: https://github.com/rainbow-me/rainbowkit/blob/main/packages/rainbowkit/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-14_snippet_21

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
import {
  getDefaultWallets,
  connectorsForWallets,
} from "@rainbow-me/rainbowkit";
import { enkryptWallet } from "@rainbow-me/rainbowkit/wallets";
const { wallets } = getDefaultWallets({ appName, chains });
const connectors = connectorsForWallets([
  ...wallets,
  {
    groupName: "Other",
    wallets: [enkryptWallet({ chains })],
  },
]);
```

